snippet.textDisplay: Tsk tsk Rose.  Bratwursts made not only made from pork, but can be made of veal or beef, too.  I live invtge kand of wurst, and most here are made from veal, which are usually lighter in color and more mild than their beef or pork siblings.  The one in the video looks likely to have been veal.   I just had a Bauernbratwurst (farmer Bratwurst made with pork) while my wife ate a Kalbbratwurst (veal bratwurst) and the two ate visually quite different.
